None
00:27:32,925 --> 00:27:35,720
Sekurang-kurangnya kita tahu majlis pelajar itu pro pelajar.

None
00:27:36,392 --> 00:27:37,519
Saya hampir terlupa.

None
00:27:37,888 --> 00:27:40,266
Gred kami dijaga.

None
00:27:40,719 --> 00:27:42,930
